Gazprom May Borrow in Chinese Yuan This Year, CFO Kruglov Says

-- B y   H a l i a   P a v l i v a
-- 
2011-02-17T18:33:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/gazprom-may-borrow-in-chinese-yuan-this-year-cfo-kruglov-says.html
OAO Gazprom may borrow in Chinese
yuan this year, Chief Financial Officer Andrey Kruglov said in  New York  today.  “We are actively working with China and expect specific
agreements this year,” Kruglov said. He declined to elaborate
further.  To contact the reporter on this story:
